icial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1118%2c20220826%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,1118,20220826,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1118","JDATE":"20220826","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}